    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事发生在一个突然爆发了战乱的大陆上，南部王国亚斯特兰遭遇了邻国戴恩的入侵，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角团为了挽救国家免于灭亡的命运，踏上了游历世界的旅途…… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/30427201de13ad8334aa12a0cbc6ee16.poster.avif?t=1729735147\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/30427201de13ad8334aa12a0cbc6ee16.webm?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/30427201de13ad8334aa12a0cbc6ee16.mp4?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作富含战略性的战斗，需要考验玩家的耐心和策略 <br>需要玩家善用各种有利地形环境进行作战。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/f4e4316f538fcf7d42871049dea7195b.poster.avif?t=1729735147\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/f4e4316f538fcf7d42871049dea7195b.webm?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/f4e4316f538fcf7d42871049dea7195b.mp4?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以各具特色的角色组成的多人小队，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个角色各有多个独特的技能，充分利用各个角色间的技能搭配，是本作战斗的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/923ec56086a169fa2ceda3f5809f253c.poster.avif?t=1729735147\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/923ec56086a169fa2ceda3f5809f253c.webm?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/923ec56086a169fa2ceda3f5809f253c.mp4?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以从中享受富含挑战和战略性的乐趣。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中设有“旅馆”，可以在商店内购物，还可以强化角色装备或武器，来提升角色们的实力。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是普通战斗胜利还是有特殊条件的战斗胜利，玩家都可以尽情享受本作的战斗乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/686d20e82ebe4b44410eef746c9465db.poster.avif?t=1729735147\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/686d20e82ebe4b44410eef746c9465db.webm?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/686d20e82ebe4b44410eef746c9465db.mp4?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
